column2: SELECT top #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.dered_u,p.dered_g,p.dered_r,p.dered_i,p.dered_z,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  gs.lgm_tot_p5# FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN galSpecExtra AS gs ON gs.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE   s.class = &&&  AND s.z > #  AND p.u > #  AND p.g > #  AND p.r > #  AND p.i > #  AND p.z > #
